{"tid":118914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建議將八仙嶺緃火案列入香港十大奇案之首！","createTime":"2017-02-13T11:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T12:30:00.000Z","uid":294,"like":159,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9aa3fcf8df1cdf0f07c9f637b0490b496e354cff","tid":118914,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T11:10:35.000Z","msg":"1. 八仙嶺緃火案<br />\n2. 雨夜屠夫<br />\n3. Hello Kitty藏屍案 <br />\n4. 屯門色魔案 <br />\n5. 溶屍案 <br />\n6. 紙盒藏屍案 <br />\n7. 康怡花園烹屍案 <br />\n8. 佳寧謀殺案 <br />\n9. 秀茂坪燒屍案 <br />\n10. 寶馬山雙屍案<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/Hk7bN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHk7bN.jpg&h=3522e9a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">死因庭：山火因煙或打火機引起！</span><br />\n<br />\n1996年八仙嶺山火是指香港新界大埔區八仙嶺於1996年2月10日發生的一場香港歷史上最被廣泛報導的山火。這場山火導致3名學生及2名老師死亡，13名學生受傷。當時的漁農處將是次山火升至最高的第3級。"},{"pid":"98aaee743eb12221041e253dc94fcf2ee75dac42","tid":118914,"uid":59965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T11:14:25.000Z","msg":"卡碧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e8d9c8e80e57152fff3e81fd172eb3cdbd24014","tid":118914,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T11:16:02.000Z","msg":"原因一：兇手逍遙法外<br />\n死因庭已表明山火因煙或打火機引起，必屬人為！<br />\n<br />\n原因二：傷亡人數最多<br />\n死亡人數：5人<br />\n受傷人數：13人<br />\n<br />\n原因三：破壞自然環境最大<br />\n焚毀面積：20公頃<br />\n<br />\n原因四：最大疑兇消費火災<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HkMuM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHkMuM.png&h=effadcb4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9223d11da7c8c952a96905c7a44d66dd39b54224","tid":118914,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T11:18:29.000Z","msg":"疑兇資料：<br />\n1. 藍白間條衫，男同學<br />\n2. 有帶火機<br />\n3. 有煙<br />\n4. 患有哮喘<br />\n5. 嚴重燒傷<br />\n6. 傷重留醫未有出席死因庭"},{"pid":"66648981f6f361330d84a8905d1d2bae225d3e8f","tid":118914,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T11:21:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c64d09a81ecffef65d0e97c0c96126127f9b4d7","tid":118914,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T11:22:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b24482d0336bcfd49e0d2b36f1c9beb3bce0f0","tid":118914,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T11:29:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔可以因為兇手犯案時未成年而逍遙法外</span><br />\n<br />\n秀茂坪燒屍案 <br />\n寶馬山雙屍案<br />\n當中都有兇手未成年, 但最終無論誤殺定謀殺都判監！"},{"pid":"10d9a51a8542006e0049e512fa8e53c6ab0bcee8","tid":118914,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T11:51:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1fdeac091a7728a7fc7364a022bbe12fd1eb45b","tid":118914,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T11:56:48.000Z","msg":"粗卡定幼卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11c747d309aba604f834890e5b70737cb25821b","tid":118914,"uid":32676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T13:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.twwiki.com/uploads/wiki/fa/2e/845397_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twwiki.com%2Fuploads%2Fwiki%2Ffa%2F2e%2F845397_3.jpg&h=af1e2a4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩尼呀"},{"pid":"074df8f88280c4aa35add7e4fd2ed9ad23153925","tid":118914,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T13:17:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"